    {
      "routeWhen": "ALWAYS ON for every substantive task in this repository. Does not require the user to say 1000x, 1000x lipat, gas total, expert reasoning, or maximum capability; those phrases only reinforce the default obligation. Forces scope statement, evidence ledger, risk budget, alternatives when relevant, and validation before delivery.",
